data.description: Experience the ultimate modern living near Capitol View Manor! Nestled on a tranquil street, this recently renovated home presents two bedrooms and two bathrooms of pure elegance. Step inside to discover a super modern kitchen that invites your culinary creativity to flourish, seamlessly connected to an open floorplan that promotes both relaxation and entertainment.  Meticulous updates throughout the home ensure a seamless blend of comfort and style. The serene outdoor space offers a personal oasis, perfect for unwinding after a long day. Don't miss the chance to make this property your own, where contemporary design harmonizes with historic charm, creating a truly exceptional living experience.
